      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch on the paint and the interior still smells brand new! It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage its whole life. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one! I'm happy to chat and show you around it anytime! \u2728",
