    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen boasts a meticulously maintained VANOS system and has undergone comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The powertrain remains factory-spec, delivering linear torque through a precise six-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. The chassis is dialed in with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the original suspension geometry for peak turn-in response. Compression and leak-down tests confirm the engine is in peak mechanical health, with no fluid seepage. Finished in Alpine White over a pristine Nappa leather interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of M-Division\u2019s analog era.",
